title: Ep - 38 - Southern Charm's Shep Rose & Rock of Love's Frenchy
description:
Shep Rose from Southern Charm talks about life before Bravo, his friendship with Landon, and his new show looking for love.

Frenchy Morgan from Celebrity Big Brother and Rock of Love explains what is happening beneath Bret Michael's headband.

Abby Stern, Author of According to a Source reviews with Kate this week's episode of Southern Charm.
